uk.ac.cam.caret.sakai.rwiki.component.radeox.service.impl

Class SpecializedRenderContext

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.radeox.engine.context.BaseRenderContext
      • uk.ac.cam.caret.sakai.rwiki.component.radeox.service.impl.SpecializedRenderContext
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    RenderContext, CachableRenderContext

    public class SpecializedRenderContext
extends BaseRenderContext
implements CachableRenderContext
    This class acts as a container for the Render context, making the RWiki Object, the Security Service and the RWikiObject service available to the Render Engine. If the operation is cachable, the RenderContext should return true
    Author:
    andrew
